node.text:
Beautiful Switzerland🇨🇭
Switzerland has traditions too!❤️
During September, the happy alp life comes to an end and the cows are going down againinto the valleys🏔🐄
They wear the big bells  only on this event🔔🤗
📹: @michelphotographych 
.
.
.

Beautiful Swiss🇨🇭
Which one from 1-10 is your favorite?☀️🏔🏡🥾☕️
Added the locations so you can add them to your bucketlist!🤗
1.From Wengen To Lauterbrunnen
2.Brienzer Rothorn Train 
3.Lake Brienz
4.Iseltwald
5.Brienz
6.Thun City of the Alps
7.Ticino 
8.Brunngasse
9.Wengen 
10.St Beatus Höhlen
📹: @michelphotographych 
.
.
.
